Sentencas: In this study, eight different samples of Tb4O7 and Eu2O3 co-doped Bi2O3 were prepared by solid-state synthesis techniques.
Titulo: Phase stability and electric conductivity of Eu2O3-Tb4O7 co-doped Bi2O3 electrolyte

Sentencas: (Bi2O3)(1-x-y)(Tb4O7)(x)(Eu2O3)(y) (x = 5,10; y = 5, 10, 15, 20 mol %) ternary systems were investigated by using X-ray powder diffraction (XRD), differential thermal analysis/thermal gravimetry (DTA/TG), and four-point probe techniques (4PPT).
Titulo: Phase stability and electric conductivity of Eu2O3-Tb4O7 co-doped Bi2O3 electrolyte

Sentencas: Effect of concentration of doping elements on the temperature and electrical conductivity was investigated.
Titulo: Phase stability and electric conductivity of Eu2O3-Tb4O7 co-doped Bi2O3 electrolyte

Sentencas: All samples were evaluated by calculating activation energies and average crystal sizes.
Titulo: Phase stability and electric conductivity of Eu2O3-Tb4O7 co-doped Bi2O3 electrolyte

Sentencas: XRD measurements show that five samples have a single phase (phase) structure.
Titulo: Phase stability and electric conductivity of Eu2O3-Tb4O7 co-doped Bi2O3 electrolyte

Sentencas: According to electrical conductivity measurements, the conductivity increases with increasing temperature but decreases with increasing amount of Eu2O3.
Titulo: Phase stability and electric conductivity of Eu2O3-Tb4O7 co-doped Bi2O3 electrolyte

Sentencas: The highest ionic conductivity was measured as 7.28 x 10(-1) (ohm.cm)(-1) for the (Bi2O3)(0.90)(Tb4O7)(0.05) (Eu2O3)(0.05) sample at 850 degrees C and the lowest activation energy was measured as 0.64 eV for (Bi2O3)(0.90)(Tb4O7)(0.05) (Eu2O3)(0.05).
Titulo: Phase stability and electric conductivity of Eu2O3-Tb4O7 co-doped Bi2O3 electrolyte
